Original R17135:                   https://svn.torproject.org/cgi-bin/viewcvs.cgi?rev=17135&view=rev

Affected Tor versions: x <= 0.2.0.32
======================
Checked both vulnerabilities present also in 0.1.2.17 and possibly older versions.

